Description: Black Falcon Productions is a full service video production company serving Portland, Oregon and the greater Northwest.
Headquarters Regions: West Coast, Western US
Full Description: Black Falcon Productions is a full service video production company serving Portland, Oregon and the greater Northwest.  We are a client-focused video production company that specializes in commercial, broadcast, live event and live web streaming. Our award-winning content is regularly aired on local and syndicated television, internet websites, news stations and national sports programs showcasing the corporations, businesses, institutions and events we cover.  Our staff is comprised of creative innovators with over 60 years of experience dedicated to the creative process of telling a compelling story.  We offer our clients the necessary tools, skills, and talent that are essential to achieving the highest level of cinematic storytelling.  These skills are a happy marriage of artistry and technical know-how.  As a full service production company, we offer video production services from script to screen. Our experience and array of sophisticated video production systems allow us to navigate all aspects of content creation and develop powerful final deliverables for our clients.  Black Falcon Productions believes you have to begin with the story before you can convey what needs to be told visually.  We focus on understanding client's needs and providing a multimedia solution including concept, planning, shooting, creative editing and delivery of product. We are budget-minded and offer different levels of production services to meet your needs.  After extensive client corroboration, we prepare a run of show or scripts that will communicate the client's message respective of the client's budget.  Only then can we begin the process of identifying the necessary equipment and cinematic processes that will yield the best method for delivering the final outcome.   Our decades of experience in live production, web streaming, webinars, commercials, music videos, and web videos enable us to identify the right equipment for the right result.  Our vast collection of state-of-the-art motion stabilized video equipment, specifically designed and tailored for land and aerial video production, enables us to accomplish the right result.  Our services include: Commercial and Broadcast Content, Game and Live Event Videography, Aerial Videography and Photography, Highlights and Award Programs, Multi-Camera Production Switching, Live or Recorded Webinars, Web-Streaming, Video production support for Advertising Agencies and other Production Companies, Green Screen Production and Commercials.  These services are augmented by an extensive collection of video production equipment, which enables us to provide our clients with a premium choice of options. With our 28 foot self-contained mobile production trailer and editing suite, we are able to work anywhere, any time.  On location, we offer the latest editing software including BlackMagic Design DaVinci Resolve, Adobe Photoshop, Adobe Premiere, Apple Final Cut Pro 7X and Avid Symphony 6.  Whether it's a live broadcast, live webcast, entertainment, sports, training video or remote location, our trailer can handle it.  We have the necessary equipment to make your next webcast look its best.  We offer HD cameras, switching, graphics and redundant HD encoders that enable us to stream in high definition and/or standard definition simultaneously. Black Falcon Productions offers our clients an aerial video production experience that is unique in the Pacific Northwest.  It starts with highly trained pilots and camera operators that have years of experience flying modern multi-rotor helicopter platforms and gyro stabilized camera gimbals. Once the flight is over, inspect your video footage or photographs on location using our full Mac-based editing suite. The Black Falcon Pilot is eco-friendly, street legal, super quiet and serves the purpose of being a low speed chase vehicle, mobile jib crane and trackless camera dolly capable of getting the smoothest video footage from on-street or off-road locations.

Full Description: Over 50 years of experience happens when you combine creative minds, passion and tenacity, mixed with dedication to what we do. We're a group of strategists, innovators, artistic misfits, media gurus and visionaries dedicated to helping your company grow.  We build experiences where people can relate to brands the same way they connect with each other. It's that emotional connection that everyone can identify with - after all, we're all customers when not working.  It's no longer feasible to just promote products and services - we need to tap into the opportunities that your brand can offer while generating an experience that people will remember. Brands are people...and people are brands. You must Be Different in order to compete. In a sea of endless mass marketing, you need to stand out from the rest. Be bold. Take chances. Invest in the possibilities - Be Different. The new reality is that your audience has changed. We no longer possess uncontested control over how a message is delivered. Your audience determines when, where, how and why they receive them, and it's up to us to make sure those messages engage people to react when it crosses their path. If people aren't emotional about your product - they aren't engaged. As stated by our strategic partner Dan Cobb at Daniel Brian Advertising, "Think about brands that make you smile. Visualize the brands that stand for your greatest ideals – your family, your values, or the healthy lifestyle you want to live. Driven by passionate purpose, these brands win consumer preference by building emotional connections." Remarkable brands show us the way. To build a leading brand, we must do more than sell your features and benefits. Let’s dream together, tap into the power of your purpose and create a movement.
